Package com.jwetherell.augmented_reality.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ARData
    Abstract class which should be used to set global data.
    BuzzDataSource
    This class extends DataSource to fetch data from Google Buzz.
    GooglePlacesDataSource
    This class extends DataSource to fetch data from Google Places.
    LocalDataSource
    This class should be used as a example local data source.
    NetworkDataSource
    This abstract class should be extended for new data sources.
    PhysicalLocation
    This class is used to represent a physical locations which have a latitude, longitude, and alitude.
    ScreenPosition
    This class is used mostly as a utility to calculate relative positions.
    TwitterDataSource
    This class extends DataSource to fetch data from Twitter.
    WikipediaDataSource
    This class extends DataSource to fetch data from Wikipedia.
